## What I Learned

Networking is the foundation of modern communication systems. Technologies such as DNS, TCP/IP, HTTP and ports work together to allow devices to exchange information over the Internet.

Understanding networking is essential in cybersecurity because attacks and defenses operate on top of network communication.

## Practical Application

To apply these concepts, I built a Python Port Scanner that identifies open ports and services running on a target system.

